OL,3,CDrivers hit by yellow box fines worth
OL,4,Calmost #1m in year
OL,6,FDrivers were fined nearly #1 million
OL,7,Ffrom just 36 yellow box junctions last
OL,8,Fyear after councils were given new
OL,9,Fenforcement powers, figures show.
OL,11,FThe RAC, which obtained the statistics
OL,12,Fthrough Freedom of Information (FoI)
OL,13,Frequests, said the "enormously high
OL,14,Fnumber" of penalty charge notices
OL,15,F(PCNs) should "send alarm bells
OL,16,Fringing in council offices".
OL,18,FYellow boxes are used in an attempt to
OL,19,Fensure traffic flows smoothly through
OL,20,Fbusy junctions.
