OL,4,Calmost #1m in year
OL,6,FMotorists should not enter them unless
OL,7,Ftheir exit is clear or they are
OL,8,Fwaiting to turn right.
OL,10,FLondon and Cardiff were the only parts
OL,11,Fof the UK where drivers could be fined
OL,12,Ffor yellow box offences until the
OL,13,FGovernment introduced new legislation
OL,14,Fin May 2022, which enables all
OL,15,Fcouncils across England to apply for
OL,16,Fenforcement powers.
OL,18,FData provided by English councils in
OL,19,Fresponse to FoI requests by the RAC
OL,20,Fshowed 36 yellow boxes outside London
OL,21,Fand Cardiff were enforced last year.
