OL,6,FThis led to a total of 32,748 PCNs
OL,7,Fissued, with drivers paying #998,640.
OL,9,FPCNs are generally #70, reduced to #35
OL,10,Fif paid within 21 days.
OL,12,FThe RAC analysis found Manchester City
OL,13,FCouncil issued the most PCNs, with
OL,14,F13,130 in relation to six junctions.
OL,16,FThis brought in #446,706 which was
OL,17,Fnearly half of all yellow box-related
OL,18,Frevenue outside London and Cardiff.
