OL,6,FKent's Medway Council raised the
OL,7,Fsecond highest amount at #145,162
OL,8,Fafter handing out 4,433 PCNs for the
OL,9,Ffive yellow boxes it enforced.
OL,11,FIt was followed by Buckinghamshire
OL,12,FCouncil, which received #139,798 for
OL,13,F3,618 fines.
OL,15,FBut the single junction that generated
OL,16,Fthe largest revenue was at Dennis
OL,17,FRoundabout in Guildford, Surrey, which
OL,18,Fcost drivers #81,445 as 4,250 PCNs
OL,19,Fwere issued.
