OL,6,FAt the other end of the scale,
OL,7,FGloucestershire County Council issued
OL,8,Fjust 30 yellow box PCNs, raising #945,
OL,9,Fwhile Leeds City Council handed out 50
OL,10,Ffines, resulting in #605 being paid.
OL,12,FOnly a fraction of yellow box fines
OL,13,Fare appealed against by drivers, with
OL,14,Fthe highest proportion appealed being
OL,15,F18% in the Manchester City Council
OL,16,Farea.
