OL,6,FRAC senior policy officer Rod Dennis
OL,7,Fsaid a yellow box which generates a
OL,8,Fsmall number of fines indicates it is
OL,9,F"working as it should", which must be
OL,10,Fthe ambition for councils rather than
OL,11,Fusing them as a "revenue-raising
OL,12,Fopportunity".
OL,14,FHe went on: "Very few people set out
OL,15,Fto deliberately flout the rules and
OL,16,Fget fined.
