OL,6,F"The large number of penalties being
OL,7,Fdished out over a small number of
OL,8,Flocations and in a short space of time
OL,9,Fshould send alarm bells ringing in
OL,10,Fcouncil offices.
OL,12,F"It's vital box junctions are used in
OL,13,Fthe correct places and are only as big
OL,14,Fas absolutely necessary.
OL,16,F"They must be fairly set up so that
OL,17,Fdrivers don't find themselves stranded
OL,18,Fthrough no fault of their own."
