OL,6,FChartered engineer Sam Wright was
OL,7,Fcommissioned by the RAC to analyse the
OL,8,F100 boxes across London and Cardiff
OL,9,Fwhich were responsible for generating
OL,10,Fthe most fines in 2019.
OL,12,FA report published last year showed he
OL,13,Ffound 98 were larger than necessary
OL,14,Ffor their role in preventing queuing
OL,15,Fvehicles blocking the path of crossing
OL,16,Ftraffic.
OL,18,FThe average box was 50% bigger than
OL,19,Fneeded, according to the research.
