OL,6,FAlex Paterson, Medway Council's
OL,7,Fportfolio holder for community safety,
OL,8,Fhighways and enforcement, said its
OL,9,Fenforcement of yellow boxes is "not
OL,10,Fabout catching people out", adding
OL,11,Fthat road markings were updated so
OL,12,F"nobody could reasonably claim not to
OL,13,Fhave seen them".
OL,15,FBuckinghamshire Council deputy leader
OL,16,FThomas Broom said the area suffers
OL,17,Ffrom "a lot of congestion" and the
OL,18,Famount of yellow box fines issued
OL,19,F"directly relates to the number of
OL,20,Fpeople who commit these traffic
OL,21,Foffences".
